com.cyc.kb

Interface LogicalConnective

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.cyc.kb.KbIndividual, com.cyc.kb.KbObject, com.cyc.kb.KbTerm, com.cyc.kb.Relation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LogicalConnectiveImpl

    public interface LogicalConnective
extends com.cyc.kb.Relation
    The interface for logical connectives of the CycL language, such as #$and and #$or. The salient property of these relations is that they take Sentences as arguments.
